creator: Ocado Retail Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Want to save time and money on your weekly supermarket shop? Find deals and do your grocery shopping quickly and easily with the Ocado app. 

Find offers on the items you buy every week, get new ideas for recipes and shop for your supermarket essentials all in one place. Ocado is the dedicated online supermarket you can fit right in your pocket. 

Food delivery, recipes and more! Why you’ll love to do your supermarket shop with Ocado: 

•  Want your food delivered tomorrow? We have a huge range of 1-hour delivery slots, between 5:30 am –11:59 pm, 7 days a week.
• You'll be spoilt for choice with every supermarket shop: enjoy our range of fresh groceries, own-label products, and much more.
• This is grocery shopping you're in control of: you can edit your order right up till the night before your food delivery.
• Add on the go: quickly add forgotten bits with One-Click.
• Browse thousands of tasty recipes: and save them for later in the app's Recipe Binder.
• We do food delivery for kitchen tables across England and parts of Wales – and we're growing all the time.
• You’ll get great value every time you buy with Ocado: our Low Price Promise means we check your comparable shopping against Tesco's listed prices online. If we're not cheaper, we’ll automatically send you a voucher for more than the difference – right up to £10.

Buy items directly from your shopping list and get them delivered instantly. From tasty recipes to all of your supermarket shop essentials, this is food shopping made simple. 

Download Ocado today: the easy way to find offers when you buy supermarket essentials and do your grocery shopping. 

Questions? Get in touch with our award-winning Customer Service team: tweet us @ocado, or find us at facebook.com/ocado, or chat with us live through the app.

To read our Privacy Policy, go to: www.oca.do/privacy
